title: The Circus - S01E20
description:
Series 1, Episode 20 of The Circus - the greatest political show on TV with a genuinely unique approach to covering this crazy election, getting access to the people that matter and really know politics.


For some reason the regular uploaders have slowed right down on this site- it's a real shame, I have had to scour all over to find this episode.

The great news is that this week is that an HD version is available - massive thanks to srigga & esc for this. Hopefully future episodes will be shared directly here in this format.


The Circus is essential viewing for every voter as it goes behind the spin and actually shines a light on the candidates - and voters should have access to it on a free to air network
